      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Some snow fell in the last seven days. <br/> Until Monday the wind will be moderate to strong. Adjacent to ridgelines and in pass areas snow depths vary greatly, depending on the infuence of the wind. <br/> The snowpack is unfavourably layered. <br/> Faceted weak layers exist in the old snowpack in particular on west, north and east facing slopes. <br/> Some medium-sized slab avalanches have been released by people in the last few days."
